org.apache.chemistry.opencmis.client.bindings.spi

Interface LinkAccess

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAtomPubService, AbstractBrowserBindingService, AclServiceImpl, AclServiceImpl, DiscoveryServiceImpl, DiscoveryServiceImpl, MultiFilingServiceImpl, MultiFilingServiceImpl, NavigationServiceImpl, NavigationServiceImpl, ObjectServiceImpl, ObjectServiceImpl, PolicyServiceImpl, PolicyServiceImpl, RelationshipServiceImpl, RelationshipServiceImpl, RepositoryServiceImpl, RepositoryServiceImpl, VersioningServiceImpl, VersioningServiceImpl

    public interface LinkAccess
    Provides access to internal links. It bypasses the CMIS domain model. Use with care!
